comments.body:
If `nullptr` is not allowed, then might as well pass const reference. Also, can erase it right away, without lookup first.

```suggestion
    void RemoveConnectionInternal(const evhttp_connection& conn) EXCLUSIVE_LOCKS_REQUIRED(m_mutex)
    { 
        m_tracker.erase(&conn);
        if (m_tracker.empty()) { 
            m_cv.notify_all();
        } 
    } 
```

